name: Adventure
description: to be adventurous; to actively seek, create, or explore novel or stimulating experiences

name: Ambition
description: aspiration, strong desire to succeed

name: Authenticity
description: to be authentic, genuine, real; to be true to myself

name: Beauty
description: to appreciate, create, nurture or cultivate beauty in myself, others, the environment, etc.

name: Compassion
description: to act with kindness towards those who are suffering

name: Courage
description: to be courageous or brave; to persist in the face of fear, threat, or difficulty

name: Creativity
description: to be creative or innovative

name: Equality
description: to treat others as equal to myself, and vice-versa

name: Freedom
description: to live freely; to choose how I live and behave, or help others do likewise

name: Fun
description: to be fun-loving; to seek, create, and engage in fun-filled activities

name: Generosity
description: to be generous, sharing and giving, to myself or others

name: Gratitude
description: to be grateful for and appreciative of the positive aspects of myself, othersand life

name: Growth
description: physical, intellectual, and spiritual development

name: Honesty
description: to be honest, truthful, and sincere with myself and others

name: Humility
description: to be humble or modest; to let my achievements speak for themselves

name: Humor
description: to see and appreciate the humorous side of life

name: Intimacy
description: to open up, reveal, and share myself - emotionally or physically

name: Justice
description: to uphold justice and fairness

name: Love
description: to act lovingly or affectionately towards myself or others

name: Patience
description: to wait calmly for what I want

name: Power
description: to strongly influence or wield authority over others, e.g. taking charge, leading, organizing

name: Respect
description: to be respectful towards myself or others; to be polite, considerate and show positive regard

name: Sexuality
description: to explore or express my sexuality

name: Spirituality
description: to connect with things bigger than myself

name: Trust
description: to be trustworthy; to be loyal, faithful, sincere, and reliable

name: Wisdom
description: experience, knowledge, and good judgement
